  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary outcome of this study is to assess if the GnRHa administration before cold loop
      hysteroscopic myomectomy contributes to accomplish the treatment in only one surgical
      procedure. Moreover, we will investigate the intraoperative influence of such pharmacologic
      therapy in terms of distension liquid absorption and duration of the procedures.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
